</div>
<div class="col-sm-9">
<p>Launch your own adventure along Canada's original highways. The lockage permit is valid for the entire navigation season and provides passage through Parks Canada’s historic canals.
</p>
<p>
<a href="http://www.commandesparcs-parksorders.ca/webapp/wcs/stores/servlet/CategoryDisplay?catalogId=53407&amp;categoryId=216871&amp;urlRequestType=Base&amp;pageView=grid&amp;urlLangId=-1&amp;beginIndex=0&amp;langId=-1&amp;currency=CAD&amp;storeId=22953">Get your lockage permits here.</a>
